fields.name: Abilities:
fields.value: - Select a target to duel each day.

fields.name: Attributes:
fields.value: - The following night, both you and your target must doxx yourselves to the host and any players in your private channel. Failure to comply means being immediately modkilled. The host decides who has a cooler looking IP Address. The other gets modkilled.

fields.name: Goal:
fields.value: Have a cooler IP Address than 2 people you dueled.
